on suggests the possibility of an inverse\nreconstruction of the underlying density field from CMB data with interesting\ntheoretical implications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Oct 1996 23:17:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-30"}
